        <h1>Melty Brands</h1>
        <div class="statement-background">
            <p class="statement">Want to eat plant-based but struggling to give cheese the boot? We hear you! Many of us at Melty enjoyed a good cheese plate back in our Standard American Diet days. And we know first hand that it’s hard to give up (but the rewards are big!).<br><br>
    
                Why is giving up cheese so difficult? It turns out, there’s science at work here. Cheese is <a target ="blank" href="https://www.mamasezz.com/blogs/news/cheese-addiction-how-to-give-up-cheese-for-good">addictive.</a><br><br>
                
                Not to mention, dairy is not the health food we grew up believing it to be! Cheese and other dairy products are inflammatory and are linked to a variety of health issues. <br><br>
                
                Yikes!<br><br>
                
                The good news- You can <a target="blank" href="https://www.mamasezz.com/blogs/news/cheese-addiction-how-to-give-up-cheese-for-good">give up cheese for good with these tips.</a><br><br>
                
                Even better news- There are so many delicious dairy-free cheese alternatives that fit better with your healthy and plant-based lifestyle.<br><br>
                Check out our featured brands, and please add your own favorite plant-based cheeses! </p>
        </div>
    </header>



